Odaily Planet Daily News According to Ember's monitoring, with the decline of Bitcoin, the long positions of the whale James Wynn except PEPE have suffered floating losses.
His 40x leverage is long 7,500 Bitcoins (worth $810 million), with an average opening price of $108,997 and a floating loss of $5.21 million;
25x leverage is long 24,506 ETH (worth $62.21 million), with an average opening price of $2,657 and a floating loss of $2.91 million;
10x leverage is long 4.85 million SUI (worth $17.51 ​​million), with an average opening price of $3.97 and a floating loss of $1.75 million.
